{"tid":597394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"$100偽鈔東涌出沒 便利店顧客中招","createTime":"2018-03-18T15:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T15:46:17.000Z","uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04bbcf36d2ae7e15f8f7d2a638386461620d52d2","tid":597394,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"一段提醒市民留意偽鈔的短片在網上流傳，拍片人表示收到三張100港元偽鈔，又指是在東涌收到。警方證實，昨日收到一名姓顧女子報案，指前日在東涌站OK便利店為八達通增值100元，給與店員500元後獲找贖回4張100元，但當中三張100港元懷疑為偽鈔，案件現交由大嶼北分區警署跟進。記者下午到過相關的便利店，店員承認昨晚有警員到場調查，但對事件不知情。<br />\n根據該段影片顯示，三張100港元懷疑偽鈔的編號分別為SZ151402、SZ151402及SZ151443，其中兩張編號相同，片中有男聲形容懷疑偽鈔「好膠吓摸落去，各位小心」。<br />\nOK便利店發言人晚上回覆《蘋果》指非常關注事件，會全力配合及協助警方調查。發言人又表示，一向有內部標準收驗鈔票程序，亦有定時安排培訓給前線服務專員。公司亦再次提醒前線同事加強對大額鈔票的核實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/225444_99df0b38145c707dcd818248b5572477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F225444_99df0b38145c707dcd818248b5572477.jpg&h=777592eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大嶼北達東路OK便利店收到三張100港元偽鈔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/225447_e2f1425fe5fccddb25cf68b28698810e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F225447_e2f1425fe5fccddb25cf68b28698810e.jpg&h=d778e020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中兩張編號相同<br />\n<br />\n估唔到一百蚊都有偽鈔，有啲似當年中國一樣<br />\n<br />\n全城用虛擬貨幣嘅日子不遠矣，即係支付寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180318/57963060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57963060&d=7qpAz7OK7EGI94xZuW%2BYpMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3100c4ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57963060&h=1e78ff56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180318/57963060</a>"},{"pid":"93b520896b6808072e0afd8d358acaf2d42086a6","tid":597394,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>東涌OK便利店疑現100元偽鈔　兩張同編號　店員：真鈔偽鈔易分辨</strong><br />\n<br />\n再有疑似假鈔出現！有網民在Facebook分享影片，指近日在東涌收到3張100元偽鈔，其中兩張編號相同，摸上手呈膠質。警方證實，一名女子昨日（17日）報案，稱前日在東涌一便利店增值後，找續到3張懷疑100元偽鈔，警方暫列「檢獲偽鈔」處理，由大嶼北分區警署跟進，未有人被捕。<br />\n記者下午曾到涉事的便利店了解，有店員私下稱涉事顧客相隔一日才報警指收到偽鈔，根本難以確認偽鈔是從便利店獲取。而有關便利店顧客服務部回應查詢指，對事件非常關注，會全力配合和協助警方調查；並已提醒前線同事加強對大額鈔票的核實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/230257_26485925de22f124c1dbce012a413cb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F230257_26485925de22f124c1dbce012a413cb3.jpg&h=7964537d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似偽鈔其中兩張的鈔票編號一樣，均是SZ151402。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n有網民在Facebook分享影片，片中有3張滙豐銀行100元鈔票，其中兩張的鈔票編號一樣，均是SZ151402，另一張是SZ151443，片中男聲指偽鈔摸上去「很膠」，呼籲大眾小心。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人證實，一名50歲姓顧女子昨日報案，稱前日在大嶼北達東路OK便利店為八達通增值100元，她給店員500元後，找回4張100元中，當中3張100元懷疑是偽鈔，警方稱事件初步未有刑事成份，暫列「檢獲偽鈔」處理，現交由大嶼北分區警署跟進，未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/230327_02e62b231ac5bfa523d9009667911e79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F230327_02e62b231ac5bfa523d9009667911e79.jpg&h=d1966dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人聲稱收到3張滙豐銀行100元鈔票，疑是偽鈔。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n店員相信閉路電視能拍攝事發過程<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者下午抵達涉事OK便利店門外，該店位於港鐵東涌站的出入口附近，顧客絡繹不絕，不時出現排隊人龍，店員幾乎｢做到無停手｣。<br />\n<br />\n記者首先以顧客身份與店員閒聊，其中一名店員證實店舖日前發生偽鈔事件，並指昨晚有警員到場了解。該店員認為，涉事顧客聲稱兩日前在便利店收到偽鈔，但又沒有即時報警，且事發相隔了兩天，根本未必可確認偽鈔是從便利店獲取，指現時是｢死無對證｣。<br />\n<br />\n另一名自稱擔任收銀員20年的女店員稱，過往從未面對過同類型事件，自己不知誰是涉事員工，並不清楚案件詳情。她認為偽鈔的質感與真鈔不同，兩者容易分辨，而且店內有閉路電視，應能拍攝事發過程。<br />\n<br />\n記者之後表明身份，再向店員了解事件詳情，惟店員們表示不便回應，着記者聯絡總公司查詢。<br />\n<br />\nOK便利店：一向有內部標準收驗鈔票程序<br />\n<br />\nOK便利店顧客服務部回應東涌分店懷疑有偽鈔一事，指非常關注今次事件，公司會全力配合和協助警方調查。該公司又指，他們一向有內部標準收驗鈔票程序，亦有定時安排培訓給前線服務專員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/169428/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8COK%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%97%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE100%E5%85%83%E5%81%BD%E9%88%94-%E5%85%A9%E5%BC%B5%E5%90%8C%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1-%E7%9C%9F%E9%88%94%E5%81%BD%E9%88%94%E6%98%93%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F169428%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258COK%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258F%25BE100%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2588%2594-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2599%259F-%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E7%259C%259F%25E9%2588%2594%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2588%2594%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25BE%25A8&d=7qpAz7OK7EGI94xZuW%2BYpMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1187ed86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/169428/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8COK%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%97%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE100%E5%85%83%E5%81%BD%E9%88%94-%E5%85%A9%E5%BC%B5%E5%90%8C%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1-%E7%9C%9F%E9%88%94%E5%81%BD%E9%88%94%E6%98%93%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8</a>"},{"pid":"993c01cb2426b7efe8abb0847eb071928399d043","tid":597394,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"262636509dcff676a2f3bba51895b441ec73c7ee","tid":597394,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"993c01cb2426b7efe8abb0847eb071928399d043","tid":597394,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"個個人心惶惶，用電子貨幣就冇憂慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n妙計"},{"pid":"c2e2322803041a20f7b39dac26bff9a2249afd3e","tid":597394,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ecc07111357e10174369fcdb79d0aee729aff0a","tid":597394,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f5aae9df422ebabe7d265720cc5c66073f897f7","tid":597394,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd169f2b4f942dcdf9d5b56bca4e8d0f1621487","tid":597394,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2e2322803041a20f7b39dac26bff9a2249afd3e","tid":597394,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"遲下50, 20都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f844901eff2a77d1895612b372dd6284e708164e","tid":597394,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd169f2b4f942dcdf9d5b56bca4e8d0f1621487","tid":597394,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2e2322803041a20f7b39dac26bff9a2249afd3e","tid":597394,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"遲下50, 20都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"上年有新聞廿蚊都有假"},{"pid":"a6d88ac035e58de4771000a194fde1930b699a52","tid":597394,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實好耐冇出新款銀紙<br />\n2003年有出款<br />\n2010年有出款<br />\n<br />\n今年2018都未有消息"},{"pid":"918760c26cccb7ec2709ad20375214331d7a1bc6","tid":597394,"uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ecc07111357e10174369fcdb79d0aee729aff0a","tid":597394,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T15:19:42.000Z","ms